name: Open The Eyes Of My Heart Lord
chorusText:
Open the eyes of my heart
I want to see you
I want to see you
1 of 3
To see You high and lifted up
Shining in the light of Your glory
Pour out Your power and love
As we sing holy, holy, holy 
2 of 3
Holy, Holy, Holy
Holy, Holy, Holy
Holy, Holy, Holy
I want to see you
3 of 3
